Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（女优小岛南的性欲）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（如何才能满足呢?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我提前做了准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这个原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉挺健康的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.63,0:00:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很健康的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天搞了三个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样子挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态超棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这么有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-已经有多久了呀? -出道还挺那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多有9年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是忘记了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.92,0:01:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.93,0:01:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也开了很多摄影吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有印象的作品有过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有印象的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.54,0:01:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有一个24小时什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个马拉松之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是这样的一个作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.49,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是做了很长的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以印象深刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.49,0:01:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.43,0:01:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分的困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也十分的舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.23,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉都是第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是感觉都舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.78,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的性欲满足吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该满足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.78,0:02:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是出作品这件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很厉害 那个欲望之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欲望跟欲求之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100%被满足的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还可以坚持吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是想去试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始做了多久?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能满足你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是未知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉呢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去的时候不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个很小的大叔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有叫出过野兽声音的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果是大叔的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没那么那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在想试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也是很难理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有摸吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是大叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙一起来就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还挺开朗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄情绪高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是并不是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.62,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是变得愉快的感觉 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能变得喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大叔里面做爱啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要怎么样才能做到呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是比较想体验这一份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是比较强烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想挑战一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性器官的大小有没有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大之类的有没有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢，果然还是越大越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢大一点的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一整天干会怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样就最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是高潮了 也不想停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就是射了一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想就此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想再来一次的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想再做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.82,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那种不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.36,0:04:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以停止的做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要 非常想要 请务必
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算中途不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不会停下来的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要挑战极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不最好了吗?请务必
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来让你满足个够吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.53,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边才是 请多指教 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（小岛南的性欲）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（能够到时候什么程度）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（才能被满足呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于准备可以开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.41,0:08:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蠢蠢欲动，停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像摄影这样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点那样子说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是性欲越来越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得越来越大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想做，还想做这样的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不搞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么骗人的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想测试一下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说你们这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有我们这几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说想超越自己的极限吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你随意地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不要紧的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了，那导演你也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当摄像机不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不需要什么台词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接做就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你比较喜欢大的对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越大越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有很多大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧，好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待
